title: Cam McCaul Mountain Bike Pre-Season Training Presented by Fox MTB
description:
Fox MTB team rider Cameron McCaul prepares for the contest season after a shoulder surgery. Catch up with Cam and watch his training session from jumps into a swimming pool to taking it straight to the dirt trails!

Music:

Artist: Dirtwire
Song: Amphibian Circuits.
